      "description": "The Building Resistance-Capacitance Modeling (BRCM) Matlab Toolbox facilitates the physical modeling of buildings for MPC. The Toolbox provides a means for the fast generation of (bi-)linear resistance-capacitance type models from basic geometry, construction and building systems data and also supports the generation of appropriate costs and constraints. The Toolbox is based on previously validated modeling principles.\r\n",
